Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:15.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... inside of Etherion...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:32.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.06,0:00:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza Scarlet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In God's grace; God fearing; her heart\Nwas as wide as the eternal sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:22.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her sword shined nobly for her loved ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:30.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her figure a dancing, fluttering fairy.\NHer beauty was a match for nature itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.45,0:02:37.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love makes us stronger, and it is \Nlove that makes us weak as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She was like a daughter to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The council has decided to award one of the \Ntwo empty council seats to her in perpetuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:06.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And name Erza Scarlet as one \Nof the 10 Wizard Saints.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:10.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.17,0:03:23.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is everyone doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:25.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:31.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza ain't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Natsu... Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell she's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:44.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Face reality, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:55.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did this for your future \Nand everyone else's, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.15,0:03:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the future I wanted to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see everyone smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...didn't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:29.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:36.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:40.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:43.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:49.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He found me inside that \Nvortex of magical power?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:05:02.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have lived without Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:07.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A world without my friends is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never do something like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.48,0:05:20.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:30.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:32.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't die for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You live for your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:48.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that's how you create a happy future!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.53,0:05:55.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's slept for three days straight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the freak \Ngets for eating Etherion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:03.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you just say, Gray?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:05.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:08.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have it in you \Nto pick a fight, don't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:13.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I really caused everyone a lot \Nof trouble this time, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, how many times \Nhave you said that already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:19.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Juvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's headed back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:26.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said something about wanting to join \NFairy Tail as soon as possible, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:35.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Er-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.38,0:06:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It was I who was not able to do \Nanything for you for eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am truly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had done something sooner, \Nthen Simon might have...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Simon was a true man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:55.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:56.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know well his feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as the feelings of those left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:07.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we must continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:09.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future that Simon left for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have no other place to \Ngo, then come to Fairy Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:21.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:26.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be different than the \N"freedom" you sought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Salamander did say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:32.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That it was one super spiffy guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:36.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd like to stay together with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:40.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:43.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to introduce you all \Nproperly to Natsu and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:47.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really gotten strong, Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:48.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.02,0:07:59.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It... couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:06.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, Erza said something \Nto me quietly in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:11.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that it might actually have been \NJellal who prevented the tower from exploding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:18.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed from Zeref's possession, he had \Nreturned to the kind Jellal he once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:23.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He then fused with Etherion in Erza's place \Nand directed the magical power up into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does make a lot of sense \Nwhen you think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kind of sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:35.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It means Jellal was just another \Nvictim of Zeref's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:36.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Sho or the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they have left without telling anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:49.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Natsu and Gray to prepare "fireworks."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think we \Ncan make it on our own?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the outside world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:11.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't bother Sister any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.56,0:09:12.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.83,0:09:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:21.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We were raised in the tower our entire lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:25.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot we don't understand, \Nthat we're uncertain of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:29.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But we want to see the \Noutside world for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want to live relying \Non others any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.39,0:09:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had enough of living for someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, we'll live for ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to find our own reason to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That{\i0} is our freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:53.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep that strong will, \Nyou can accomplish anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:55.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It reassures me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are three conditions for \Nanyone who leaves Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:04.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave? But we never even joined...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:08.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:13.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never reveal sensitive information \Nabout Fairy Tail to others for as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:14.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:19.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not have unauthorized contact with \Npast clients or profit personally from them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:20.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:26.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we walk different paths, one must \Nalways live on as strong as you are able!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never treat your own \Nlife as something insignificant!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:39.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must never forget the friends \Nyou love for as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:45.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin the Fairy Tail Farewell Ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let bloom the flowers of \Nlight within your hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be with you forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.13,0:11:19.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that ends up holding you back, then \NI wish to bless your newfound voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it backwards, Er-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:27.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With us around, you'll be forced \Nto remember all the bad things...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget you, no \Nmatter where you may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:35.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And it is those painful memories \Nthat become the seeds of tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They make us stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans have that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:43.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will continue on, stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.03,0:11:49.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we never forget this \Nday, we will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:52.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Er-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:19.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They finished it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Our new Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an outdoor cafe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a goods shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:32.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Oh, it's you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:32.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you're a salesman now, Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, how long has it been again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:41.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been out studying \Nbusiness on Master's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Max Aloze? You've been in Weekly Sorcerer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've just met, glad to be of service.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard quite a lot about you, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even want to imagine \Nwhat he's heard about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:52.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so what are you selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-shirts, wrist bands, mugs, towels...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the most popular is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a figure of Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:02.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making something like \Nthat without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, the clothes are cast-off! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:17.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different than it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lu-chan, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:25.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, huh? In the back of \Nthe drinking hall is a pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:31.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a game parlor in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:32.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:35.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:36.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}different{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the biggest change is the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can go up there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:48.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you still have to be with an\NS-class wizard to go on an S-class quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've returned, you bunch of fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:56.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our new member, Juvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't she a cutey?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is glad to be of service!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:03.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you really joined?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:05.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You helped us a lot at Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.40,0:14:09.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia will work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Love rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have one more new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.55,0:14:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, say hi to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're got to be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:28.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia recommended him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.02,0:14:38.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Juvia is one thing, but he's the \Nvery person who destroyed the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They say yesterday's enemies \Nare tomorrow's friends, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.05,0:14:47.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I d-don't mind at a-all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has got to be some joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You expect me to go on jobs with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:54.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't sharing my work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold as steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want jobs, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I ended up here in \Nthe most annoying guild of all... 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Gajeel-kun was always all alone, and \NJuvia couldn't leave him like that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that kind of \Nrelationship though, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the role of we elders to guide youth \Nfrom the wrong path to the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, even he is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...or so I'd like to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's your decision, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:29.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think it best to watch \Nhim carefully for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:35.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're more like dogs \Nthan dragons, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:39.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's even lower than cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't feel at home here anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:49.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:51.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:57.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now sing a song commemorating the \Nnew guild and to welcome back Natsu's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting, Mira!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best, Mirajane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:17.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I brush the desk with you gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:25.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow drops...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alone again, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:47.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking up at the starry \Nsky, I say a prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:17:00.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now under this same sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:58.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you all are back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:08.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you're shaking with tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:16.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even when it seems like you'll \Nbe lost to the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's children are \Nsure to continue to grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.61,0:17:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be time for me to \Nstart thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:22.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Don't forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:29.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.45,0:17:37.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have a place to return to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:53.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You always have people \Nwaiting for you to return...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:10.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote this song myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:12.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called "Best Friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you choke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:15.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you all dolled up in a suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Colorful, colorful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooby doo bop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.96,0:18:24.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tremble with love, steel grey metallic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:25.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got chops!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it, Gajeel-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doo doo doo... Shalala...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:35.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooby doo bop! Shalala...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bite into it, hard! Sweet honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:41.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard a song this crappy before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shooby do bop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shooby doo bopping, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who threw that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're goin' overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My... strawberry cake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:05.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Real men don't make such a damn racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:22.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is more like Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal calling me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about going out on a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:37.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A job?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the guy who destroyed the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.70,0:19:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got no right to a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.17,0:19:42.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys sure are petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.89,0:19:45.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... don't hold any grudges at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...settle the score!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:59.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be feeling so confident for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Secret Seeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knuckle Plant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Falcon Heaven's Soar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you playing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of bullying is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:31.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the kid that \Ndid a number on my guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So gramps let someone join to keep \Nthe guild from being busted up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:41.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why people look down on us! 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little piece of...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,On the road back to town, I heard things in \Nbars here and there that really pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fairy Tail ain't anything special..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those guys are already through..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:14.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Laxus! That's going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew Laxus is crazy strong, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that one-sided?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is it that Gajeel never even...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he wanted us to \Nrecognize him as an ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:28.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He just took it, without defending himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:34.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you what happens to \Nanybody who takes on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.61,0:21:38.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Laxus! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:40.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The weaklings should stay outta this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.03,0:21:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gajeel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:57.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.97,0:22:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiocy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the Fairy Tail I have in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:18.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take this any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail will be mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.65,0:23:59.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A tournament to decide the \Nstrongest in Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Erza and Laxus will be in it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'll win, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:06.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.49,0:24:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:11.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "gnats" to a flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:12.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.67,0:24:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Battle of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:20.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't giving you squat when I win, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, your temper will be your downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.43,0:24:24.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
